iant','2025-10-04 16:51:16'),(76,'1526626586',14,'VISION_LABEL_MISSING','Product label not clearly visible',0,'medium','Could not detect clear product labels in images | Recommendation: Ensure product labels are clearly visible in images','2025-10-04 16:51:16'),(77,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_MRP_DECLARATION','MRP Declaration',0,'medium','MRP is mandatory for electronics and should be clearly displayed on the packaging. While the listed price is present, it is not confirmed if the packaging contains an MRP declaration as per Legal Metrology rules. | Recommendation: Ensure the packaging clearly displays the MRP, including the phrase \'Maximum Retail Price\' or \'MRP (Incl. of all taxes)\'.','2025-10-04 17:08:54'),(78,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_MANUFACTURER_ADDRESS','Manufacturer Address',0,'low','While the manufacturer\'s name is provided, the address is missing. Legal Metrology rules require the full address of the manufacturer to be available. | Recommendation: Include the complete address of Padget Electronics Pvt Ltd in the product description or on the packaging.','2025-10-04 17:08:54'),(79,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_NET_QUANTITY_DECLARATION','Net Quantity Declaration',0,'low','While the phone\'s storage (128GB) and RAM (6GB) are mentioned, the actual net quantity (i.e., one smartphone) should be explicitly declared. | Recommendation: Explicitly mention \'1 unit\' or \'1 piece\' in the product description or on the packaging to denote the net quantity.','2025-10-04 17:08:54'),(80,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_COUNTRY_OF_ORIGIN','Country of Origin',1,'low','The country of origin (India) is provided. | Recommendation: Compliant','2025-10-04 17:08:54'),(81,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_GENERIC_NAME','Generic Name',1,'low','The generic name \'Smartphone\' is provided. | Recommendation: Compliant','2025-10-04 17:08:54'),(82,'B0F9TT7Z5Q',17,'GEMINI_MANUFACTURER_NAME','Manufacturer Name',1,'low','Manufacturer name, Padget Electronics Pvt Ltd, is provided. | Recommendation: Compliant','2025-